


{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": "iot:Connect",
      "Resource": "*"
    },
    {
      "Effect": "Allow",
      "Action": "iot:Publish",
      "Resource": "arn:aws:iot:your-region:your-account-id:topic/attendance/scan"
    }
  ]
}
AWS IoT Core Console > Security > Policies.
Go back to your Certificate (under Security > Certificates), click Actions > Attach Policy, and select the one you just created.
